													</p>
													<h4>About the job:</h4>
													<ul>
														<li>
															Full time positions
														</li>
														<li>
															Pay determined on
															experience and
															skills
														</li>
														<li>
															Certifications are
															preferred either
															from manufacturers,
															ASE, or other
															training
															institutions
														</li>
														<li>
															Willingness to learn
															and good team skills
															are a must!
														</li>
													</ul>
													<p></p>
												</div>
												<h4>What we offer:</h4>
												<ul>
													<li>
														GREAT PAY! We pay well
														to keep good people!!
													</li>
													<li>
														5 days a week,
														8am-5:00pm
													</li>
													<li>No weekends</li>
													<li>Paid Birthday off</li>
													<li>Personal days</li>
													<li>
														Paid training days and
														continuing education
													</li>
													<li>
														Well staffed with
														knowledgeable techs and
														service writers
													</li>
													<li>Uniforms provided</li>
													<li>
														Heated and well
														ventilated shop
													</li>
													<li>
														Clean, modern,
														professional facility
														with modern diagnostic
														equipment provided
